Earn One Mile for Every Net Purchase Dollar! Our TWA MasterCard and
Visa cards work twice as hard! TWA and European American Bank (EAB®)
offer a credit card that rewards you with outstanding benefits and Frequent
Flight Bonus (FFB®) miles. You'll receive one TWA FFB mile for every net
purchase dollar charged to the card. You can exchange your FFB miles to
travel to exciting cities and exotic islands all over the world on TWA and its
partner airlines!
Unlike many other frequent flyer programs, TWA miles have no expiration
date. And, when you charge your TWA tickets to the card, you'll earn miles for
every net purchase dollar you spend PLUS travel miles. ***
Take off with a 3,000 Mile Bonus! Apply for the TWA credit card today and
upon the first purchase with your card, we'll give you a special sign-up bonus
of 3,000 miles.
FREE $50 Flight Certificate! Save $50 off the first TWA ticket you charge to
the card (minimum published fare $250).**
Automatic Purchase Protection. Most new purchases and gifts charged
entirely to the card are automatically protected against theft and accidental
damage for 90 days from the date of purchase, and extended warranty
doubles the manufacturer's original or store brand warranty for up to one
additional year.
First Class Travel Benefits. Charge travel expenses to the card and enjoy
the added security of these benefits: Worldwide Acceptance...$150,000
